autoroute

Class DrillPageArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • autoroute.DrillPageArray

  • public class DrillPageArray
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes the 2 dimensional array of pages of ExpansionDrill`s used in the maze search algorithm. The pages are rectangles of about equal width and height covering covering the bounding box of the board area.
    Version:
    $Id: $Id
    Author:
    Alfons Wirtz
